<section class="sto-plus">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title-h2 sto-plus__title">100+ Satisfied Clients</h2>
    <img class="sto-plus__img" src="img/100plus__img.svg" alt="" />
    <p class="text-p2 sto-plus__description">
      At G&D Consulting, we have successfully helped numerous clients in
      overcoming financial, tax, and accounting challenges. With a growing base
      of over 100 satisfied clients, our team of experts is well-equipped with
      the essential knowledge and expertise to prevent errors, ensure
      compliance, and capitalize on opportunities that others might overlook. By
      efficiently managing time-consuming tasks, we enable our clients to focus
      on their core business objectives and personal endeavors. <br />
      <br />
      Our commitment to cost-effectiveness and security has earned us the trust
      of a wide range of clients. We provide top-notch services without
      compromising on quality or the safeguarding of your confidential
      information. Our transparent and prompt communication guarantees clients
      remain well-informed and supported throughout our collaboration.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="work-together">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title-h2 work-together__title">Let’s work together!</h2>
    <form class="form" action="/submit" method="post">
      <input
        type="text"
        id="name"
        name="name"
        placeholder="Your name"
        required
      />
      <input
        type="email"
        id="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="Your Email"
        required
      />
      <select
        name="request"
        id="request"
        placeholder="What is your request"
        required
      >
        <option value="request" checked>What is your request?</option>
        <option value="Accounting Services">Accounting Services</option>
        <option value="Tax Consulting">Tax Consulting</option>
        <option value="Financial Consulting">Financial Consulting</option>
      </select>
      <textarea
        id="message"
        name="message"
        placeholder="Tell more about your request"
      ></textarea>
      <button class="btn-main form__btn">Send</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="contact">
  <div class="line-star__image">
    <img class="line-star__img" src="img/star-line.svg" alt="" />
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title-h2 contact__title">Or you can contact with us</h2>
    <div class="contact__btns">
      <button class="whatsapp__btn">Whatsapp</button>
      <button class="telegram__btn">Telegram</button>
      <button class="email__btn">E-mail</button>
    </div>
    <p class="text-p2 contact__text">
      Click for a free consultation and confidently achieve financial goals.
      Empower your business with our expert services. Act now!
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

